Earning Online Without a Website
Each and every day, an average of $86 million changes hands through eBay auctions. Every 
day, an estimated 2 million people use eBay to buy things they can not find in stores, or to get 
rid of things they do not use any more in order to make room in their house. But did you know 
that 430,000 eBay? run a full or part-time business from their homes? Of course, there are the 
big product sellers, who auction off things like new cars, real estate, or computers. However, 
there are also normal people running eBay? business from their homes, not only selling things 
that are no longer needed around the house, but selling everyday consumer goods, and making 
a full-time income from it.
